summary:
Founded Backpack (YC, S14), one of the largest cross-border marketplaces in the world, backed by Y Combinator, Khosla Ventures, SV Angels and scaled the team from 2 to 50+ people.

A decade of software engineering experience, with 6+ years as engineering leader/manager. I enjoy working at the junction of engineering, product and management. Passionate about building 0->1 products and scaling teams.
